author: Fellshard

text: +Fellshard I discovered Skaven on modarchive or some other chiptune/mod site about 8 or 9 years ago, and I barely figured out sometime in 2012 that he also did video game music. I played a lot of Alchemy when I was younger, I don't know how that eluded me for so long. He was one of my earliest inspirations for composing electronically. I still put OpenMPT on all my computers, even though I rarely use it.
